  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for xen",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for xen fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-42487: x86 HVM I/O port list traversal (bsc#1266952).\n- CVE-2026-42488: x86: mismatched mapcache metadata (bsc#1266955).\n- CVE-2026-42489,CVE-2026-42490: domctl lock open to abuse (bsc#1266953).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
